SQL is a relational database and mongodb is a non-relational database.

In SQL we perfotm CRUD operations:

Create
Read
Update
Delete

SQL full form : Structured Query Laguage

SQL is also known as SEQUEL(Structured English Query Language) , this language is made by IBM.

Genaral Order

SELECT columns
FROM table_name
WHERE conditions
GROUP BY columns
HAVING conditions
ORDER BY columns

SET SQL_SAFE_UPDATES = 0; (this commands help to turn off safe mode in sql so that we update it)

SET SQL_SAFE_UPDATES = 1; (this commands help to turn on safe mode in sql)

DROP command is used to delete the table but TRUNCATE is used to delete data from table

Join is used to combine rows from two or more tables, based on a related column between them
